item.summary: IllegalArgumentException: JBAS014577: Unsupported marshalling version: 1 on shutdown

status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.

comments.comment: This error occurs about 50% of the time (sometimes different tests) in our CI runs on brontes...
The service providing the infinispan cache for the EJB deployment is missing a dependency on the service that provides the marshalling configuration.
